OL,3,CWhy might employers now be sued if
OL,4,Cthey don't take menopause seriously?
OL,6,FThe watchdog has issued the guidance
OL,7,Fto clarify the legal obligations to
OL,8,Fworkers going through the menopause.
OL,10,FResearch shows that one in 10 women
OL,11,Fwho have worked during the menopause
OL,12,Fhave left their jobs due to symptoms,
OL,13,Fthe watchdog said.
OL,15,FWhat are the symptoms of menopause and
OL,16,Fhow will this new guidance be
OL,17,Fimplemented? ITV News explains.
OL,19,FWhat is the menopause?
