OL,3,CWhy might employers now be sued if
OL,4,Cthey don't take menopause seriously?
OL,6,FEmployment Law expert Kate Palmer
OL,7,Ftells ITV News what the new guidance
OL,8,Fmeans for people struggling with
OL,9,Fsymptoms of the menopause
OL,11,FWhat are the symptoms?
OL,13,FSymptoms of menopause can begin months
OL,14,F- or even years - before your periods
OL,15,Factually stop and can affect people in
OL,16,Fdifferent ways.
OL,18,FThere are both mental health symptoms
OL,19,Fand physical symptoms that indicate
OL,20,Fyou are going through the menopause.
OL,21,FThe most common symptoms include:
