OL,3,CWhy might employers now be sued if
OL,4,Cthey don't take menopause seriously?
OL,6,FThe perimenopause is when you have
OL,7,Fsymptoms of menopause, but your
OL,8,Fperiods have not stopped. It ends and
OL,9,Fyou reach menopause when you have not
OL,10,Fhad a period for 12 months.
OL,12,FWhat is the new guidance?
OL,14,FThe new guidance, published on
OL,15,FThursday, has been issued by the EHRC.
