OL,3,CWhy might employers now be sued if
OL,4,Cthey don't take menopause seriously?
OL,6,FUnder the Equality Act 2010, an
OL,7,Femployer will be under a legal
OL,8,Fobligation to make reasonable
OL,9,Fadjustments and to not discriminate
OL,10,Fagainst the worker.
OL,12,FThose experiencing menopause symptoms
OL,13,Fmay additionally be protected from
OL,14,Fless favourable treatment related to
OL,15,Ftheir menopause symptoms on the
OL,16,Fgrounds of age and sex, the watchdog
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,19,FWhat do employers have to do?
