OL,3,CWhy might employers now be sued if
OL,4,Cthey don't take menopause seriously?
OL,6,FBosses should consider how room
OL,7,Ftemperature and ventilation affect
OL,8,Fmenopausal women and think about
OL,9,Fproviding rest areas or quiet rooms,
OL,10,Fas well as cooling systems or fans for
OL,11,Fwomen experiencing hot flushes, the
OL,12,Fguidance says.
OL,14,FIt adds that women could be helped by
OL,15,Fflexible working, including being
OL,16,Fallowed to work from home, and start
OL,17,Fand finish times should be varied if a
OL,18,Fwoman has had a bad night's sleep or
OL,19,Fon a warmer day.
