OL,3,CWhy might employers now be sued if
OL,4,Cthey don't take menopause seriously?
OL,6,FRelaxing uniform policies or allowing
OL,7,Fmenopausal women to wear cooler
OL,8,Fclothes could also be a way of helping
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,FWhat happens if employers don't make
OL,12,Fthese adjustments?
OL,14,FFailing to make "reasonable
OL,15,Fadjustments" will amount to disability
OL,16,Fdiscrimination under the act if a
OL,17,Fworker's menopause symptoms amount to
OL,18,Fa disability, the watchdog said.
