OL,3,CWhy might employers now be sued if
OL,4,Cthey don't take menopause seriously?
OL,6,FHow does this differ from previous
OL,7,Fguidance?
OL,9,FSome employers across the UK have
OL,10,Fpledged to adopt menopause-friendly
OL,11,Fpolicies in the workplace.
OL,13,FIn 2022, the NHS, for instance, issued
OL,14,Fguidance that nurses and doctors
OL,15,Fshould get uniforms in a breathable
OL,16,Ffabric to help with hot flushes.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/13
