OL,3,CWhy might employers now be sued if
OL,4,Cthey don't take menopause seriously?
OL,6,FSymptoms of menopause that meet this
OL,7,Fcriteria amount to a disability,
OL,8,Faccording to the EHRC. Employers are
OL,9,Funder a legal obligation to make
OL,10,F"reasonable adjustments" when this is
OL,11,Fthe case.
